{
  "stem": "14091.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "After a very short time, they caught my brother and they sent him to the front.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "By the way, being in the partisans, before my brother came to retrieve me, my older brother was with him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was wounded in the knee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And Zalman, my brother, organized-- of course, you had to bribe and do many things-- and they sent him out one of the planes to Russia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when Zalman came for me, to retrieve me, my brother was already saved.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This what we hoped, that he was in Russia, saved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he was useless to the partisans because he-- his knee was shot, and he couldn't walk or he couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- my brother and I were liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came to our town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after a very short time, they took him to-- to Russia front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I did not know if [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Tzila, ?] my sister, where she was or if she-- if she survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But many, many people start coming to the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And not too many, but the people who survived, everybody came to look for others who maybe, by some miracle, survived too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there, and one of the newcomers was my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Piotr was also taken to the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tzila's ?] friend, Piotr, was also taken there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't know how it happened that my brother got out-- Zalman-- and he came to us, to our town, and he became-- he start working for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- we start searching for my brother in Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
